vote.title: A resolution authorizing the Mayor to appoint an Ad Hoc City Council Canvassing Committee to review the returns of the Tuesday, November 8, 2022 special election, and submit a canvass report to the full City Council on Wednesday, November 16, 2022 City Council meeting or at a special called city council meeting - Financing:  No cost consideration to the City
